- cs.SD (Sound): One of the tasks tackled in the paper is Arabic dialect identification in speech broadcasts, which involves analyzing sound data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of machine learning and ensemble methods in the paper falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): Language and dialect are important factors in social networks and communication, and the paper's focus on identifying language and dialect varieties could be relevant to this sub-category.
